data.title: Highly Suspect premieres new song 'My Name Is Human,' exclusively on Octane
data.meta_description: Grant Random premieres new Highly Suspect song My Name Is Human, exclusively on Octane (Ch. 37)!
data.text:
Cape Cod-bred hard rock trio Highly Suspect are prepping the release of their highly anticipated second full-length album.

First played by Octane (Ch. 37) as an emerging group back in 2015 with their single Lydia, they went on to become an Octane Accelerator band and ultimately won Octane’s Discovery of the Year Award.

Octane is excited to be one of the first to share new music from the band, starting this morning as Grant Random premiered their latest single My Name Is Human.

“This isn’t a song, it’s a wake-up call,” frontman Johnny Stevens said of the track.

Hear it on Octane!
